主体人工文字/主体人工文字_0039.jpg.mt:
Compared to non-elastic weight-added processed silk quilts,  
more fluffiness, more elasticity!  

Friendly Reminder:  
Silk quilts on the market with poor fluffiness and elasticity often undergo weight-adding processes,  
as silk is sold based on its weight.  
Currently, some unscrupulous merchants unlawfully use silk cotton weight-adding processes.  
For instance, a 4-pound silk quilt may only contain 3 pounds of silk,  
while the remaining 1 pound consists of slippery oil-based chemical additives absorbed onto the silk fibers.  
After testing, the free formaldehyde content may severely exceed the standard.
src: 比无弹性的增重处理的蚕丝被
更有蓬松性 更有弹性！
友情提醒：市场上有蓬松度弹性很差的蚕丝被，有增重处理，蚕丝都是按蚕丝重量卖的，现有不法商家违法使用丝绵增重处理，可能4斤的蚕丝被，只有3斤的蚕丝，余下1斤是吸附在蚕丝纤维上的润滑油性化学增重剂。
经检测，基蛋白质氨基酸含量严重不达标。
